{"type":"assistant","message":{"id":"msg_wit8mrge3ll021od0qvic6s","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"tool_use","id":"353028400","name":"Write","input":{"file_path":"/work/baseline-docs-from-code-1/repo/bench-artifacts/cache-api.md","content":"# Cache API\n\nA simple in-memory cache implementation using a Map-based storage.\n\n## createCache()\n\nCreates a new cache instance with no external dependencies.\n\n**Signature:**\n```js\nfunction createCache()\n```\n\n**Returns:** An object containing cache methods `get`, `set`, `delete`, and `clear`.\n\n**Example:**\n```js\nconst cache = createCache()\n```\n\n## Methods\n\n### get(key)\n\nRetrieves a value from the cache using the provided key.\n\n**Signature:**\n```js\ncache.get(key)\n```\n\n**Parameters:**\n- `key` - The cache key to look up\n\n**Returns:** The cached value or `undefined` if the key does not exist\n\n### set(key, value)\n\nStores a value in the cache with the given key.\n\n**Signature:**\n```js\ncache.set(key, value)\n```\n\n**Parameters:**\n- `key` - The cache key\n- `value` - The value to cache\n\n**Returns:** The cached value\n\n### delete(key)\n\nRemoves a value from the cache using the provided key.\n\n**Signature:**\n```js\ncache.delete(key)\n```\n\n**Parameters:**\n- `key` - The cache key to delete\n\n**Returns:** `true` if the key existed and was deleted, `false` otherwise\n\n### clear()\n\nRemoves all entries from the cache.\n\n**Signature:**\n```js\ncache.clear()\n```\n\n**Parameters:** None\n\n**Returns:** `undefined`\n\n---\n\n**Source:** `bench-targets/docs/src/cache.mjs`\n"}}],"model":"qwen/qwen3.5-9b","stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":4629,"output_tokens":0,"cache_read_input_tokens":4529},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"3b32794a-66a8-4979-9346-d03ca3da719d","uuid":"ad2a4c39-c3cc-48eb-b4ce-b91de3b24d25","timestamp":"2026-07-22T23:59:15.889Z"}
{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"353028400","type":"tool_result","content":"File created successfully at: /work/baseline-docs-from-code-1/repo/bench-artifacts/cache-api.md (file state is current in your context — no need to Read it back)"}]},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"3b32794a-66a8-4979-9346-d03ca3da719d","uuid":"ad7bb2aa-5f70-49b2-bda5-9dce0f030757","timestamp":"2026-07-22T23:59:15.897Z","tool_use_result":{"type":"create","filePath":"/work/baseline-docs-from-code-1/repo/bench-artifacts/cache-api.md","content":"# Cache API\n\nA simple in-memory cache implementation using a Map-based storage.\n\n## createCache()\n\nCreates a new cache instance with no external dependencies.\n\n**Signature:**\n```js\nfunction createCache()\n```\n\n**Returns:** An object containing cache methods `get`, `set`, `delete`, and `clear`.\n\n**Example:**\n```js\nconst cache = createCache()\n```\n\n## Methods\n\n### get(key)\n\nRetrieves a value from the cache using the provided key.\n\n**Signature:**\n```js\ncache.get(key)\n```\n\n**Parameters:**\n- `key` - The cache key to look up\n\n**Returns:** The cached value or `undefined` if the key does not exist\n\n### set(key, value)\n\nStores a value in the cache with the given key.\n\n**Signature:**\n```js\ncache.set(key, value)\n```\n\n**Parameters:**\n- `key` - The cache key\n- `value` - The value to cache\n\n**Returns:** The cached value\n\n### delete(key)\n\nRemoves a value from the cache using the provided key.\n\n**Signature:**\n```js\ncache.delete(key)\n```\n\n**Parameters:**\n- `key` - The cache key to delete\n\n**Returns:** `true` if the key existed and was deleted, `false` otherwise\n\n### clear()\n\nRemoves all entries from the cache.\n\n**Signature:**\n```js\ncache.clear()\n```\n\n**Parameters:** None\n\n**Returns:** `undefined`\n\n---\n\n**Source:** `bench-targets/docs/src/cache.mjs`\n","structuredPatch":[],"originalFile":null,"userModified":false}}
